<template>
1
</template>

<script>
import { useRoute } from 'vue-router'
import { reactive, toRefs } from 'vue'
import { get } from '../../utils/request'

const useBookInfoEffect = () => {
  const route = useRoute()
  const data = reactive({ list: [] })
  const getBookInfo = async () => {
    const result = await get('/allTabBook', { tab: route.params.tab })
    if (result) {
      data.list = result
    }
  }
  const { list } = toRefs(data)
  return { getBookInfo, list }
}

export default {
  name: 'AllTabBook',
  setup () {
    const { list, getBookInfo } = useBookInfoEffect()
    getBookInfo()
    return { list }
  }
}
</script>

<style lang="scss" scoped>
</style>
